When LOGO! BM is in RUN mode, BM publishes LOGO! time data value every 10 seconds. The 
LOGO! time data value can be concluded in a message that contains other data values. The 
following are examples of messages containing LOGO! time data value: 
•  LOGO! time data value in hex string format (Compatible to 8.3 cloud data format): 
{ 
 "state": { 
 "reported": { 
 "I..1:1-1": "00", 
 "V..2:990-6": "282303060313" 
 } 
 } 
} 
•  LOGO! time data value in integer array format: 
{ 
 "state": { 
 "reported": { 
 "I": { 
 "desc": "I-bit-1-1", 
 "value": [ 
 0 
 ] 
 }, 
 "$logotime": 1678072448 
 } 
 } 
} 
